SideWays:

SideWays had heard enough. "Descepticons of the future, you make me sick, you 
belly ache over the most ignorant things, I'd blast you both, but i'm afraid 
one of you might actually be a grandchild of mine." He shook his silver head 
which hoped off and Rook the black one took its place. "Allow me to welcome you 
to this world, I am SideWays of the Cybertronian Decepticons of the year 
2003."

--part1_198.1af64f43.2c082af2_boundary
